  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with tumors in liver or pancreas are randomized to ultrasound (UL)-guided FNAC
      biopsies with guidance method or UL-guided FNAC biopsies with free-hand method.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
